item.title: Plz help me
item.dc:creator: @bullzeye95 bullzeye
item.description:
@bullzeye95 wrote:

Ok don’t use si.scar, it’s outdated. Use SRL

Try this: [scar]program Autominer;
{.include srl/srl.scar}

Procedure minerocks;
Begin
repeat
Findcolor(x,y,7565691,274,166,515,340);
Mouse(x,y,1,1, true);
Wait(5000);
until(invfull)
if(invfull)then
repeat
dropall;
until(invcount=0)
End;

Begin
setupsrl;
repeat
minerocks;
until(false)
end.
[/scar]
